section.section:
The committee shall be composed of the following:
The adjutant general, as an ex officio voting member;
The commissioner of the Department of Veterans' Affairs, as an ex officio voting member;
The executive director of the Commission on Military Affairs, as an ex officio voting member;
The executive director of the Historical Society, as an ex officio voting member; and
Twelve (12) members appointed by the Governor under paragraph (b) of this subsection.
